title: Product Snapshot: Navigator 2.0
description:
Feel the freedom of this styling digital compass with our proprietary free fit technology, a nonrestrictive permeable material which allows the buckle tongue to insert at any point along the band assuring a perfect fit for any wrist.
100 Meters H20
Declination Adjustment
Time/Calendar
30 Lap Memory Chrono
Timer with 2 interval timers
3 Alarms
Digital compass with 16 cardinal directions and digital direction with 1 degree resolution.
Live Free. Freestyle.
